              <p class="title-font">mindlevelup</p>
              <img src="images/mlu.png" class="image-in-desc"/>
              <p>
                <a href="https://mindlevelup.wordpress.com/">mindlevelup</a> is a blog about human rationality; it's a look at how humans make decisions and how we might be able to make better ones. New essays come out almost every week, ranging from somewhat well-researched to purely speculative. Topics cover habits, planning, motivation, and introspection.
              </p>
              <p>
                For a more structured overview, I’ve also written a book that’s adapted much of its content from the blog posts. That’s freely available <a href="essays/mindlevelupBook.pdf">here</a>.
              </p>
              <img src="images/screenshots/mindlevelup.png" class="primer-image image-border"/>
              <br />
          </div>



